# Crop config for 《牡丹亭·拾畫叫畫》 — 石小梅 recording (096折子戲, 720x576 4:3 VCD).
# Lyrics sit bottom-center (~y 467-517). Tuned via `./run_play.sh probe`.
#
# NOTE: an earlier CIBN 1920x1080 recording of the same play used a different
# crop (X560 Y833 W800 H95); that run is archived under shihuajiaohua_old/.
# This env now targets the 720x576 石小梅 source. Command-line CROP_* overrides.
CROP=on
CROP_X=108
CROP_Y=467
CROP_WIDTH=510
CROP_HEIGHT=50
